I am pleased to announce that our company has been identified as Leader in the ISG Provider Lens™ Quadrant study on “Insurance Services - Strategic Capabilities 2025” for the Insurance ITO Services Specialists quadrant.
ISG has launched their research on "Insurance Services – Strategic Capabilities 2025" ISG Provider Lens™ Study. This study will evaluate providers on their ability to deliver the technology and services most important to their enterprise clients.
For this year’s study, ISG is covering the following 7 quadrants across 1 region. We can choose to respond only against those quadrant(s) and geo(s) that is/ are most favorable for us.
1. Insurance GCC CaaS: Setup-Run-Optimize-Transform-Transfer
2. genAI - Development and Deployment Services
3. Agentic AI - Development and Deployment Services
4. Life and Retirement (L&R) Insurance Services Specialists
5. Property and Casualty (P&C) Insurance Services Specialists
6. Insurance ITO Services Specialists
7. Insurance Digital Engineering Services
